  <h2>How to Use This Calculator</h2>

  <h3>Single Discount tab</h3>
  <p>Enter the <strong>original price</strong> and <strong>discount percentage</strong>. The calculator instantly shows the final price and how much you save. Use this for straightforward sales — "30% off," "25% discount," etc.</p>

  <h3>Double Discount tab</h3>
  <p>For stacked discounts — like "extra 20% off sale items." Enter the <strong>original price</strong>, the <strong>first discount</strong>, and the <strong>second discount</strong>. The calculator applies them sequentially and shows the final price, total savings, and the effective combined discount (which is always less than the sum of the two).</p>

